3EThe%20discovery%20of%20body%20parts%20of%20a%20missing%20child%20in%20a%20drain%20near%20Pandher's%20home%20led%20to%20a%20massive%20investigation%20that%20revealed%20the%20identities%20of%20more%20victims.%20Disturbing%20allegations%20of%20murder%2C%20mutilation%2C%20and%20even%20cannibalism%20held%20the%20nation's%20attention%20for%20weeks%20and%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20there%20were%20a%20series%20of%20gruesome%20murders%20of%20several%20more%20children%2C%20after%20which%20the%20case%20was%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESurinder%20Koli%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20several%20children%20at%20his%20employer's%20house.%20Koli%20had%20earlier%20confessed%20to%20having%20sex%20with%20the%20dead%20victims%20and%20also%20eating%20their%20body%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20was%20also%20convicted%20for%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2020-year-old%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697790900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fj4g0urkk_nithari-serial-killings-accused-moninder-singh-pandher-ani_625x300_20_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnithari-killings-accused-moninder-singh-pandher-released-from-jail-4499225%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nithari's%20serial%20killings'%20accused%20Moninder%20Singh%20Pandhar%20was%20released%20from%20a%20Greater%20Noida%20jail%20today%20days%20after%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20Court%20cleared%20him%20of%20all%20charges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnithari-killings-accused-moninder-singh-pandher-released-from-jail-4499225%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnithari-killings-accused-moninder-singh-pandher-released-from-jail-4499225%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnithari-killings-accused-moninder-singh-pandher-released-from-jail-4499225%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maratha%20Quota%20Stir%3A%20Man%20Dies%20by%20Suicide%2C%20Leaves%20Note%20Demanding%20Reservation%20for%20Community%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30123722%2FIllustration-Pariplab-Chakraborty.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20grave%20development%20in%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20protests%20that%20started%20late%20August%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fmaharashtra-quota-suicide-poses-new-challenge-for-eknath-shinde-govt%2Farticleshow%2F104563975.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ea%C2%A045-year-old%20man%20died%20by%20suicide%3C%2Fa%3E%20demanding%20reservations%20for%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESunil%20Kavle%2C%20a%20Maratha%20activist%20from%20Jalna%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fmaharashtra-quota-suicide-poses-new-challenge-for-eknath-shinde-govt%2Farticleshow%2F104563975.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eleft%20a%20three-page%20suicide%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%20stating%20that%20he%20was%20ending%20his%20life%20seeking%20reservations%20for%20his%20community%20before%20hanging%20himself%20from%20a%20a%20flyover%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20death%20comes%20just%20five%20days%20before%20the%20deadline%20set%20by%20Maratha%20leader%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil%20who%20has%20threatened%20a%20wider%20agitation%20if%20the%20Marathas%20were%20not%20recognised%20as%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20by%20October%2024%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fmaharashtra-quota-suicide-poses-new-challenge-for-eknath-shinde-govt%2Farticleshow%2F104563975.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKavle%E2%80%99s%20family%20said%20that%20the%20government%20should%20honour%20his%20last%20wishes%20and%20provide%20reservations%20to%20the%20Marathas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20(state)%20government%20is%20responsible%20for%20this.%20There%20is%20a%20view%20within%20the%20community%20that%20the%20government%20is%20deliberately%20not%20giving%20Marathas%20reservations.%20The%20government%20should%20not%20keep%20the%20Marathas%20waiting%20but%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20given%20reservations%20soon.%20I%20am%20imploring%20the%20Maratha%20youth%20to%20not%20take%20any%20drastic%20steps.%20We%20will%20have%20a%20peaceful%20stir%20but%20we%20will%20get%20reservation%20for%20our%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Patil%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fmaharashtra-quota-suicide-poses-new-challenge-for-eknath-shinde-govt%2Farticleshow%2F104563975.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20another%20Maratha%20youth%20ended%20his%20life%20seeking%20quota%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fexplainer-why-the-maratha-quota-agitation-has-put-successive-maharashtra-governments-in-a-bind%5C%22%3EExplainer%3A%20Why%20the%20Maratha%20Quota%20Agitation%20Has%20Put%20Successive%20Maharashtra%20Governments%20in%20a%20Bind%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fmaharashtra-quota-suicide-poses-new-challenge-for-eknath-shinde-govt%2Farticleshow%2F104563975.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20a%20totally%20insensitive%20government.%20Under%20this%20triple%20engine%20government%2C%20they%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20give%20reservation%20to%20the%20Dhangar%20(shepherd)%20community%2C%20Muslims%2C%20Lingayats%20and%20Marathas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Maratha%20quota%20protests%20had%20begun%20on%20August%2029%20when%20Patil%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fexplainer-why-the-maratha-quota-agitation-has-put-successive-maharashtra-governments-in-a-bind%5C%22%3Ea%20Maratha%20activist%20from%20Jalna%2C%20sat%20on%20an%20indefinite%20hunger%20strike%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20reviving%20a%20three-decade%20old%20demand%20for%20Maratha%20reservations.%20In%20some%20places%2C%20the%20agitation%20turned%20violent%20with%20the%20police%20resorting%20to%20lathi-charge%20on%20the%20protesters%2C%20further%20worsening%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20government%20apologised%20for%20the%20lathi-charge%20and%20later%20announced%20that%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20will%20be%20issued%20to%20those%20who%20possess%20revenue%20or%20education%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fthose-with-nizam-era-documents-recognising-them-as-kunbis-to-get-caste-certificates-cm-shindee%5C%22%3Edocuments%20from%20the%20Nizam%20era%20that%20recognise%20them%20as%20Kunbis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20solution%20was%20not%20accepted%20by%20Patil%20and%20his%20supporters.%20On%20October%2014%2C%20the%20maratha%20leader%20gave%20a%20deadline%20to%20the%20state%20government%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2023%2F10%2F14%2Fbom6-mh-maratha-quota-jarange.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20October%2024%2C%20it%20will%20be%20either%20my%20funeral%20procession%20or%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20victory%20celebration%20(after%20granting%20of%20reservation).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20activist%20said%20he%20would%20address%20the%20community%20on%20October%2022%20to%20explain%20their%20course%20of%20action%20after%20October%2024%20in%20case%20the%20demand%20is%20not%20fulfilled.%20He%20also%20asked%20his%20supp