-finke-1235762971%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fskyshowtime-juan-mayne-kai-finke-1235762971%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fskyshowtime-juan-mayne-kai-finke-1235762971%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mahua%20Moitra's%20Lawyer%20Withdraws%20After%20Court's%20Rap%20For%20Playing%20%26quot%3BMediator%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMahua%20Moitra's%20defamation%20plea%20over%20'cash-for-query'%20allegations%20against%20her%20will%20be%20heard%20by%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20on%20October%2031.%20The%20case%20was%20postponed%20after%20her%20lawyer%20today%20withdrew%20from%20the%20case%20citing%20a%20'conflict%20of%20interest'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20withdrawal%20came%20after%20the%20court%20was%20informed%20by%20advocate%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20that%20Ms%20Moitra's%20lawyer%20Gopal%20Sankarnarayan%20contacted%20him%20over%20phone%20on%20Thursday%20night%20for%20withdrawing%20his%20complaint%20to%20the%20CBI%20against%20the%20Trinamool%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20has%20described%20Mr%20Dehadrai%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bjilted%20ex%26quot%3B%20who%20wants%20to%20get%20back%20at%20her.%20There%20is%20an%20ongoing%20tussle%20between%20Ms%20Moitra%20and%20Mr%20Dehadrai%20over%20their%20pet%20dog%2C%20Rottweiler%20Henry.%20In%20the%20last%20six%20months%2C%20Ms%20Moitra%20has%20filed%20multiple%20police%20complaints%20against%20Mr%20Dehadrai%20for%20alleged%20criminal%20trespass%2C%20theft%2C%20vulgar%20messages%20and%20abuse%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Dehadrai%20had%20provided%20alleged%20evidence%20to%20BJP%20leader%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20of%20Ms%20Moitra%20accepting%20cash%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20the%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20'conflict%20of%20interest'%20was%20brought%20up%20in%20court%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20on%20Thursday.%20Justice%20