0painting%20titled%20%26quot%3BLandscape%20of%20Italian%20Character%26quot%3B%20by%20Vienna-born%20artist%20Johann%20Franz%20Nepomuk%20Lauterer%2C%20Thursday%2C%20Oct.%2019%2C%202023%20in%20Chicago.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6531faf5be9edfa8eda57a5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20baroque%20landscape%20painting%20stolen%20by%20a%20US%20soldier%20was%20returned%20to%20a%20German%20museum.%3Cp%3EClaire%20Savage%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20stolen%20painting%20was%20returned%20to%20Germany%20after%20going%20missing%20for%20over%2078%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20FBI%20recovered%20the%20painting%20after%20a%20company%20enlisted%20their%20help%20in%20retrieving%20it%20from%20a%20Chicago%20resident.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ESomeone%20had%20previously%20tried%20to%20sell%20the%20painting%20in%20the%20Chicago%20art%20market%20in%202011.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20stolen%20painting%20belonging%20to%20Germany%20made%20an%20unusual%20journey%20home%20on%20Thursday%20after%20going%20missing%20for%20over%2078%20years%2C%20according%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fbi.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Fmissing-since-world-war-ii-painting-repatriated-to-bavarian-museum%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20returned%20the%20painting%20to%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20Alte%20Pinakothek%20museum%20at%20the%20German%20consulate%20in%20Chicago.%20The%20artwork%20was%20first%20reported%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fpainting-stolen-world-war-ii-american-germany-c6d9850c9f934cd9dcb74d01e2989448%5C%22%3Estolen%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Bavarian%20State%20Paintings%20Collections%20in%20Munich%20in%201945.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20%26quot%3BLandscape%20of%20Italian%20Character%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20painting%20by%20the%20Vienna-born%20artist%20Johann%20Franz%20Nepomuk%20Lauterer%2C%20per%20the%20FBI.%20The%20painting%20was%20created%20in%20the%20early%2018th%20century%2C%20making%20it%20over%20300%20years%20old%20now%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theartnewspaper.com%2F2023%2F10%2F19%2Fbavaria-recovers-a-baroque-painting-with-help-from-the-fbi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Art%20Newspaper%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20artwork's%20value%20has%20not%20been%20publicly%20evaluated%20by%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EItaly-based%20Art%20Recovery%20International%20helped%20recover%20the%20item%20after%20a%20Chicago%20resident%20informed%20the%20company%20their%20uncle%20owned%20a%20stolen%20painting%2C%20the%20company's%20founder%20Christopher%20Marinello%20told%20Insider.%20The%20resident's%20uncle%2C%20who%20has%20since%20died%2C%20obtained%20the%20artwork%20after%20serving%20in%20World%20War%20II%2C%20Marinello%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20person%2C%20who%20has%20not%20been%20identified%20in%20reports%2C%20tipped%20off%20Marinello%20in%20December%202022%2C%20per%20The%20Art%20Newspaper.%20Marinello%20confirmed%20to%20Insider%20that%20the%20person%20asked%20his%20company%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bfinder's%20fee%26quot%3B%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20artwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20pay%20money%20to%20possessors%20of%20stolen%20art%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20circumstances%20of%20how%20this%20artwork%20came%20into%20the%20family's%20possession%2C%26quot%3B%20Marinello%20said.%20He%20then%20enlisted%20the%20FBI's%20art%20crime%20team%20for%20help%20retrieving%20the%20painting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarinello%20told%20Insider%20that%20an%20individual%20%E2%80%94%20whom%20he%20believes%20is%20the%20same%20person%20who%20tipped%20him%20off%20about%20the%20stolen%20painting%20%E2%80%94%20had%20previously%20tried%20to%20sell%20it%20in%20the%20Chicago%20art%20market%20in%202011.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20told%20it%20was%20stolen%20property%2C%20he%20withdrew%20and%20disappeared%2C%26quot%3B%20Marinello%20said.%20Insider%20could%20not%20independently%20verify%20this%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlte%20Pinakothek%20and%20researchers%20at%20Art%20Recovery%20International%20verified%20the%20painting%20as%20being%20Lauterer's%20original%20artwork%20in%202022%2C%20Marinello%20told%20Insider.%20It%20will%20be%20displayed%20at%20the%20Alte%20Pinakothek%20alongside%20another%20painting%20by%20Lauterer%20featuring%20similar%20motifs%20of%20the%20Italian%20countryside%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pinakothek.de%2Fen%2Fpresse%2Fwiedervereinigung-zweier-barockgemaelde%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20museum%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20a%20stolen%20painting%20has%20been%20recovered%20from%20US%20soldiers%20who%20served%20in%20World%20War%20II.%20In%202015%2C%20the%20FBI%20recovered%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2015%2F05%2F06%2Farts%2Fdesign%2Freturning-the-spoils-of-world-war-ii-taken-by-our-side.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20artworks%20stolen%20by%20US%20soldiers%20from%20a%20German%20museum%20in%20Dessau%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20city%20in%20central%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20office%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fart-stolen-us-world-war-ii-germany-painting-soldier-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697789363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6531faf5be9edfa8eda57a5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus