%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmarriage-equality-supreme-court-decision%5C%22%3Edeclined%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20legalise%20same-sex%20marriage%20and%20left%20it%20to%20the%20parliament%20to%20decide%20on%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3En%20its%20petitions%20to%20the%20top%20court%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20opposed%20same-sex%20marriages.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Furban-elitist-views-centre-files-affidavit-in-sc-opposing-same-sex-marriages%5C%22%3Ehad%20argued%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage%20is%20%E2%80%9Cexclusively%20heterogenous%E2%80%9D%20and%20those%20seeking%20same-sex%20marriages%20represent%20%E2%80%9Curban%20elitist%20views%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20social%20acceptance%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20said%20that%20same-sex%20marriage%20is%20not%20%E2%80%9Ccomparable%20with%20the%20Indian%20family%20unit%20concept%20of%20a%20husband%2C%20a%20wife%20and%20children%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20while%20delivering%20the%20judgment%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmarriage-equality-supreme-court-decision%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CQueerness%20is%20not%20urban%20or%20elite.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20an%20English%20speaking%20man%20with%20a%20white%20collar%20man%20who%20can%20claim%20to%20be%20queer%20but%20equally%20a%20woman%20working%20in%20an%20agricultural%20job%20in%20a%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6Queerness%20can%20be%20regardless%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20caste%20or%20class%20or%20socio-economic%20status.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-8%5C%22%3EPrevious%20US%20State%20Department%20reports%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freut.rs%2F42vuoqn%5C%22%20data-testid%3D%5C%22Link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20raised%20concer