0in%20India.%20I%20hope%20this%20award%20will%20serve%20as%20a%20flicker%20of%20hope%20to%20several%20other%20younger%20journalists%2C%20my%20colleagues%20at%20AltNews%20and%20the%20readers%20of%20AltNews.%20Lastly%2C%20I%20want%20to%20thank%20everyone%20who%20stood%20by%20me%20when%20I%20was%20attacked%2C%20slandered%20and%20even%20jailed%20for%20doing%20my%20job.%20Thank%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Zubair%20was%20nominated%20last%20month%2C%20the%20Index%20referred%20to%20his%20arrest%20in%20June%202022%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20representative%20of%20the%20significant%20threats%20he%20has%20faced%20after%20challenging%20mis%20and%20disinformation%20propagated%20by%20influential%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndex%20on%20Censorship%20CEO%20Ruth%20Anderson%20had%20said%20said%20that%20the%C2%A0Freedom%20of%20Expression%20Awards%20are%20a%20%E2%80%9Cchance%20to%20recognise%20the%20astonishing%20work%20being%20done%20in%20extraordinary%20circumstances%20by%20artists%2C%20journalists%2C%20and%20campaigners%20around%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20awards%20they%20give%20are%20across%20four%20categories%20of%20Arts%2C%20Campaigning%2C%20Journalism%20and%20the%20Trustee%20award.%20The%20other%20two%20nominees%20on%20the%20shortlist%20were%20Bilan%20Media%2C%20which%20is%20Somalia%E2%80%99s%20first%20women-only%20media%20organisation%20and%20newsroom%2C%20and%20Afghan-French%20journalist%20and%20filmmaker%20Mortaza%20Behboudi%20who%20was%20forced%20to%20leave%20Afghanistan%20in%20his%20youth%20due%20to%20previous%20threats%20as%20a%20result%20of%20his%20reporting%2C%20and%20was%20detained%20by%20the%20Taliban%20in%20January%20in%20Kabul.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Sophia%20Huang%20Xueqin%20received%20the%20award.%20She%20is%20a%20Chinese%20activist%20and%20journalist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndex%20on%20Censorship%20is%20based%20in%20London%20and%20also%20brings%20out%20a%20quarterly%20magazine%20devoted%20to%20calling%20out%20censorship%20and%20standing%20for%20free%20expression.%20Poet%C2%A0Stephen%20Spender%20was%20closely%20associated%20with%20this%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697780714000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20105552%2FMZ1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmohammad-zubair-of-altnews-hopes-his-index-on-censorship-award-will-be-a-flicker-of-hope%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Index%20on%20Censorship%20while%20awarding%20him%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20share%20in%20his%20campaign%20for%20transparent%20and%20accurate%20news.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmohammad-zubair-of-altnews-hopes-his-index-on-censorship-award-will-be-a-flicker-of-hope%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20to%20start%20giving%20shape%20to%20semiconductor%20research%20centre%20from%202024%3A%20Min%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697780659000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F09%2Ffull%2F1691604359-1486.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fgovt-to-start-giving-shape-to-semiconductor-research-centre-from-2024-min-123102000236_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BA%20group%20of%20top%20minds%20in%20semiconductor%20around%20the%20world%20and%20country%20have%20sat%20together%20to%20design%20the%20Bharat%20Semiconductor%20Research%20Centre%2C%26quot%3B%20Chandrasekhar%20told%20PTI%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fgovt-to-start-giving-shape-to-semiconductor-research-centre-from-2024-min-123102000236_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-s