20video%20was%20shot%20on%20Gurugram%E2%80%99s%20Golf%20Course%20Road%20and%20acts%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%20another%20incident%20involving%20a%20Hyundai%20Verna%20in%20October%202022.%20The%20Verna%20was%20also%20treated%20as%20a%20rocket%20launcher%20with%20a%20pack%20of%20firecrackers%20strapped%20to%20its%20boot%20lid.%20However%2C%20in%20this%20case%20the%20police%20were%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20owners%20using%20the%20registration%20plate%20details%20and%20arrested%20three%20and%20seized%20two%20cars.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22AMBER%20BANERJEE%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fnews%2Fviral-video-ford-endeavour-converted-into-rocket-launcher-in-gurugram%2Farticleshow%2F104571980.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canada%20Confirms%20Withdrawal%20of%2041%20Diplomats%20From%20India%2C%20Visa%20Processing%20Time%20to%20Go%20Up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Canada%20on%20Thursday%20(October%2019)%20has%20stated%20that%2041%20diplomats%20have%20left%20India%20after%20New%20Delhi%20demanded%20%E2%80%98parity%E2%80%99%20over%20diplomatic%20representation%20as%20it%20lashed%20out%20over%20Ottawa%E2%80%99s%20allegation%20of%20Indian%20agents%20being%20involved%20in%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20national.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20Canada%20will%20stop%20the%20in-person%20visa%20services%20in%20all%20three%20consulates%20at%20Mumbai%2C%20Chandigarh%C2%A0and%20Bengaluru%2C%20while%20the%20overall%20visa%20processing%20time%20for%20Indian%20nationals%20will%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20likely%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20largest%20withdrawal%20of%20diplomats%20from%20a%20single%20country%20at%20one%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20response%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20till%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Canada%20had%20expelled%20an%20Indian%20diplomat%20after%20accusing%20New%20Delhi%20of%20being%20potentially%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20NIjjar%2C%20a%20Khalistan%20supporter.%20Angrily%20dismissing%20the%20charges%2C%20India%20had%20also%20expelled%20a%20Canadian%20diplomat%2C%20stopped%20all%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadians%20and%20asked%20Ottawa%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20number%20of%20diplomats%20in%20line%20with%20Indian%20diplomatic%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanadian%20foreign%20minister%20M%C3%A9lanie%20Joly%C2%A0said%20that%20India%20had%20formally%20communicated%20its%20plan%20to%20remove%20diplomatic%20immunity%20from%20most%20of%20its%20diplomats%20by%20October%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20means%2041%20Canadian%20diplomats%20and%20their%2042%20dependents%20were%20in%20danger%20of%20having%20immunities%20stripped.%20Given%20the%20security%20implications%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20actions%20on%20these%20Canadian%20diplomats%20and%20their%20families%2C%20Canada%20has%20facilitated%20their%20safe%20departure%20from%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Joly%20told%20reporters%20in%20Ottawa.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20consular%20team%20has%20now%20been%20drastically%20reduced.%20%E2%80%9CFive%20IRCC%20staff%20(Immigration%2C%20Refugees%20and%20Citizenship%20Canada)%20remain%20in%20India%20and%20will%20focus%20on%20work%20that%20requires%20an%20in%C2%AD-country%20presence%20such%20as%20urgent%20processing%2C%20visa%20printing%2C%20risk%20assessment%20and%20overseeing%20key%20partners%2C%20including%20visa%20application%20centres%2C%20panel%20physicians%20and%20clinics%20that%20perform%20immigration%20medical%20exams.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20work%20and%20staff%20will%20be%20reassigned%20across%20our%20global%20processing%20network.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Canadian%20media%20reports%20quoting%20unnamed%20officials%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Canadian%20staff%20who%20will%20deal%20with%20consular%20work%20has%20been%20decreased%20from%2027%20to%20five.%20They%20review%20applications%20not%20just%20from%20India%2C%20but%20also%20Nepal%20and%20Bhutan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2F41-canadian-diplomats-left-india-1.7001515%5C%22%3ECanadian%20officials%20stated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2045%25%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20international%20students%2C%2027%25%20of%20new%20permanent%20residents%20and%2022%25%20of%20temporary%20foreign%20workers%20come%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20Canada%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20pause%20all%20in-person%20services%20in%20the%20consulates%2C%20Joly%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CImmigration%2C%20Refugees%20and%20Citizenship%20Canada%20(IRCC)%20will%20continue%20to%20accept%20and%20process%20applications%20from%20India.%20However%2C%20certain%20application%20requirements%20will%20need%20to%20be%20completed%20locally%20or%20on-site%20in%20a%20secure%20environment.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20reduction%20in%20the%20size%20of%20the%20IRCC%20team%20will%20affect%20service%20standards%20for%20residents%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanadian%20media%20had%20earlier%20reported%20that%20India%20had%20given%20a%20deadline%20of%20October%2010%20for%20downsizing%20its%20embassies%2C%20but%20that%20deadline%20passed%20without%20any%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20meanwhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F37165%2FTranscript_of_Weekly_Media_Briefing_by_the_Official_Spokesperson_October_05_2023%5C%22%3Ereiterated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20will%20pursue%20diplomatic%20parity%20with%20Canada%20%E2%80%9Cgiven%20the%20much%20higher%20diplomatic%20presence%20of%20Canadian%20diplomats%20or%20diplomatic%20presence%20here%20of%20Canada%20and%20their%20continuing%20interference%20in%20our%20internal%20affairs%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20India%20had%20not%20publicly%20announced%20a%20deadline%20for%20the%20return%20of%20the%20Canadian%20diplomats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20announcement%20in%20Ottawa%2C%20Joly%20had%20described%20India%E2%80%99s%20threat%20to%20unilaterally%20revoke%20diplomatic%20immunity%20as%20contrary%20to%20international%20law%2C%20including%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20action%20taken%20by%20India%20is%20completely%20unreasonable%20and%20escalatory.%20India%20accredited%20each%20and%20every%20one%20of%20the%20Canadian%20diplomats%20they%20are%20now%20expelling.%20And%20all%20of%20those%20diplomats%20were%20carrying%20out%20their%20duties%20in%20good%20faith%2C%20and%20to%20the%20greater%20benefit%20of%20both%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20diplomatic%20immunities%20cannot%20be%20unilaterally%20revoked%20by%20host%20country%2C%20Joly%20noted%20that%20if%20this%20norm%20was%20broken%2C%20%E2%80%9Cno%20diplomat%20anywhere%20would%20be%20safe%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20stated%20that%20Canada%20will%20not%20reciprocate%20Indian%20actions.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20such%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20Canada%20will%20continue%20to%20respect%20diplomatic%20norms%20and%20not%20reciprocate%20this%20action.%20Canada%20will%20continue%20to%20defend%20international%20law%2C%20which%20applies%20equally%20to%20all%20states.%20Canada%20will%20continue%20to%20engage%20India%20and%20remains%20committed%20to%20dialogue%20as%20we%20move%20forward.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20foreign%20minister%20also%20reiterated%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20decision%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20not%20distract%20from%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20legitimate%20investigation%20into%20the%20killing%20of%20Mr.%20Nijjar%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCanada%E2%80%99s%20priorities%20in%20this%20matter%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20pursuit%20of%20the%20truth%2C%20the%20protection%20of%20Canadians%2C%20and%20the%20defence%20of%20our%20sovereignty%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697779003000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-confirms-withdrawal-of-41-diplomats-from-india-visa-processing-time-to-go-up%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canada%20will%20stop%20the%20in-person%20visa%20services%20in%20all%20three%20consulates%20at%20Mumbai%2C%20Chandigarh%C2%A0and%20Bengaluru.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-confirms-withdrawal-of-41-diplomats-from-india-visa-processing-time-to-go-up%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20a%20U-Turn%2C%20Union%20Govt%20Rolls%20Back%20Plans%20to%20License%20Laptop%2C%20Computer%20Imports%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20103256%2Fales-nesetril-Im7lZjxeLhg-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Union%20government%20on%20Thursday%20(October%2019)%20officially%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20not%20be%20sticking%20to%20its%20earlier%20plan%20of%20imposing%20import%20restrictions%20on%20laptops%2C%20tablets%2C%20and%20certain%20types%20of%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20notification%2C%20the%20government%20announced%20a%20new%20%E2%80%98import%20management%20system%E2%80%99%20for%20IT%20hardware.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fgovt-tweaks-licensing-norms-laptop-computer-imports-place-online-authorisation-system-8990566%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20under%20the%20new%20regulations%2C%20%E2%80%9CIT%20hardware%20companies%20will%20be%20required%20to%20register%20and%20disclose%20data%20related%20to%20their%20imports%2C%20and%20countries%20from%20which%20they%20import%2C%20among%20other%20things.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20had%20been%20worried%20by%20a%20previous%20licensing%20notification