apparel%2C%20offer%20prayers%2C%20and%20gather%20to%20celebrate%20unity%20and%20devotion.%20Smriti%20Irani%2C%20an%20actor%20turned%20politician%2C%20dedicated%20a%20post%20on%20Instagram%20to%20the%20well-being%20of%20children%20and%20offered%20her%20prayers%20on%20the%20sixth%20day%20of%20Navratri.%20Netizens%20reacted%20positively%20to%20her%20post%2C%20with%20one%20user%20expressing%20blessings%20for%20all%20children.%20Take%20a%20look%20at%20her%20post%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22etimes.in%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fsmriti-irani-pens-a-special-note-for-durga-puja-writes-on-shasti-as-every-mother-prays-for-the-well-being-of-her-children-i-offer-my-prayers-to-ma%2Farticleshow%2F104571683.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MGNREGA%20Sees%20Record%20Job%20Card%20Deletions%20in%202022-23%20Due%20to%20%E2%80%98Violation%20in%20Procedure%E2%80%99%2C%20Finds%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F03131216%2FScreen-Shot-2021-11-03-at-1.07.58-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20research%20organisation%20has%20noted%20a%20record%20increase%20in%20the%20deletion%20of%20job%20cards%20for%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20database%20last%20financial%20year%20of%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Frule-flout-stink-in-job-card-purge-glare-on-5-crore-nrega-deletions-in-a-year%2Fcid%2F1974481%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20various%20state%20governments%20deleted%20over%205%20crore%20job%20cards%20from%20the%20MGNREGA%20database%20in%202022-23%2C%20suggesting%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20due%20procedure.%20This%2C%20per%20LibTech%20India%2C%20is%20far%20higher%20than%20the%20yearly%20average%20of%201%20crore%20to%201.5%20crore%20deletions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELibTech%20India%20focuses%20on%20various%20aspects%20of%20improving%20transparency%2C%20accountability%2C%20and%20democratic%20engagement%20in%20rural%20public%20services%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELibTech%20India%20conducted%20a%20field%20verification%20by%20interviewing%2C%20between%20October%202022%20and%20June%202023%2C%20600%20workers%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Jharkhand%20whose%20cards%20had%20been%20deleted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20found%20that%20rules%20were%20flouted%20in%20all%20600%20deletions%20and%20that%20the%20reasons%20cited%20were%20incorrect%20in%20380%20instances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20governments%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20this%20was%20routine%20updation%2C%20citing%20reasons%20such%20as%20duplicate%20or%20fake%20cards%2C%20deaths%2C%20and%20cardholders%E2%80%99%20unwillingness%20to%20work%20under%20the%20scheme%20any%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaavanya%20Tamang%2C%20a%20LibTech%20India%20researcher%2C%20cited%20the%20huge%20jump%20in%20deletions%20in%202022-23%20to%20suggest%20a%20deliberate%20paring%20of%20numbers%20by%20state%20governments%2C%20which%20faced%20pressure%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20ensure%20that%20MGNREGA%20wage%20payments%20were%20made%20through%20the%20Aadhaar%20Based%20Payment%20System%20(ABPS).%20She%20said%20ensuring%20ABPS%20compliance%20would%20have%20meant%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20for%20the%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20seems%20the%20states%20accelerated%20the%20deletion%20of%20job%20cards%20as%20the%20Union%20rural%20development%20ministry%20insisted%20on%20100%20per%20cent%20ABPS%20compliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tamang%20told%20the%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20ABPS%20compliance%2C%20a%20worker%E2%80%99s%20Aadhaar%20number%20must%20be%20linked%20to%20their%20job%20card%20and%20bank%20account%2C%20which%20is%20facilitated%20by%20the%20state%20government%20and%20linked%20to%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20institutional%20identification%20number.%20States%20might%20have%20found%20deletion%20the%20easiest%20option%20to%20avoid%20this%20cumbersome%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20master%20circulars%20(AMCs)%20issued%20under%20the%20MGNREGA%20allow%20job%20card%20cancellations%20on%2013%20specific%20grounds.%20However%2C%20any%20addition%20or%20deletion%20of%20job%20cards%20must%20be%20presented%20before%20the%20gram%20sabha%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETamang%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20field%20verification%20exercise%20had%20found%20that%20the%20gram%20sabhas%20were%20not%20consulted%20in%20any%20of%20the%20600%20deletions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJob%20cards%20can%20be%20cancelled%20if%20the%20holder%20applies%20for%20deletion.%20The%20panchayat-level%20MGNREGA%20official%20can%20also%20do%20so%20after%20informing%20the%20gram%20sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(states)%20mentioned%20reasons%20like%20not%20willing%20to%20work%20or%20not%20present%20in%20the%20panchayat%20in%20most%20of%20the%20cases.%20After%20verification%2C%20we%20found%20the%20reasons%20cited%20in%20the%20official%20documents%20were%20not%20true%20in%20the%20case%20of%20380%20of%20the%20600%20workers%20interviewed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tamang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20daily%20sent%20an%20email%20to%20rural%20development%20secretary%20Shailesh%20Kumar%20Singh%20on%20October%205%2C%20asking%20whether%20the%20charges%20of%20wrongful%20deletion%20were%20true%20and%2C%20if%20so%2C%20what%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20done%20about%20it.%20His%20response%20is%20awaited.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Faadhaar-mgnrega-errors-corruption%5C%22%3EAadhaar%20in%20MGNREGA%20Is%20Likely%20to%20Be%20Hugely%20Disruptive%20for%20Workers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Rural%20Development%20(MoRD)%20mandated%20the%20use%20of%20ABPS%20for%20processing%20all%20wage%20payments%20in%20MGNREGA%2C%20starting%20from%20February%201%2C%202023.%20However%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20mandate%2C%20only%2043%25%20of%20MGNREGA%20workers%20were%20eligible%20for%20ABPS%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20pressure%20from%20MoRD%20to%20achieve%20100%25%20Aadhaar%20seeding%20(the%20process%20of%20workers%20submitting%20their%20Aadhaar%20details%20to%20be%20linked%20to%20their%20job%20cards)%20and%20authentication%20in%20a%20short%20period%20led%20to%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20worker%20deletions%20from%20the%20MGNREGA%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERural%20development%20minister%20Giriraj%20Singh%2C%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20July%2025%2C%202023%2C%20had%20said%20the%20total%20deletion%20of%20MGNREGA%20job%20cards%20stood%20at%205.18%20crore%20in%202022-23%20against%201.5%20crore%20in%202021-22.%20In%202022-23%2C%20Bengal%20topped%20the%20list%20with%20the%20deletion%20of%2083%20lakh%20job%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20various%20reasons%20for%20the%20deletion%20of%20job%20cards%20are%20given%20below%3A%20i.%20fake%20job%20card%20(incorrect%20job%20card)%20ii.%20duplicate%20job%20card%20iii.%20now%2C%20not%20willing%20to%20work%20iv.%20family%20shifted%20from%20Gram%20Panchayat%20permanently%20v.%20single%20person%20in%20job%20card%20and%20the%20person%20is%20expired%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said%20in%20the%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697777916000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F03131216%2FScreen-Shot-2021-11-03-at-1.07.58-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmgnrega-sees-record-job-card-deletions-in-2022-23-due-to-violation-in-procedure-finds-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Various%20state%20governments%20deleted%20over%205%20crore%20job%20cards%20from%20the%20MGNREGA%20database%20in%20the%20last%20financial%20year%2C