a%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Joly%20added.%20%26quot%3BThis%20means%20that%20our%20diplomats%20and%20their%20families%20have%20now%20left.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERelations%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20have%20plunged%20since%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20last%20month%20publicly%20linked%20Indian%20intelligence%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Canadian%20citizen%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20which%20New%20Delhi%20has%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%2C%20who%20advocated%20for%20a%20separate%20Sikh%20state%20carved%20out%20of%20India%2C%20was%20wanted%20by%20Indian%20authorities%20for%20alleged%20terrorism%20and%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRevoking%20the%20diplomatic%20immunity%20of%2041%20diplomats%20is%20not%20only%20unprecedented%2C%20but%20also%20contrary%20to%20international%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Joly%20said%20Wednesday%2C%20but%20said%20Canada%20did%20not%20plan%20to%20retaliate%20in%20kind%2C%20so%20as%20to%20not%20%26quot%3Baggravate%20the%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCanada%20will%20continue%20to%20defend%20international%20law%2C%20which%20applies%20to%20all%20nations%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20engage%20with%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20more%20than%20ever%20we%20need%20diplomats%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20we%20need%20to%20talk%20to%20one%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20Joly%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Countermeasures%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20called%20for%20India%20to%20cooperate%20in%20the%20investigation%20but%20New%20Delhi%20has%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20and%20taken%20countermeasures%2C%20such%20as%20shutting%20down%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOttawa%20also%20expelled%20an%20Indian%20diplomat%20over%20the%20affair.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Subrahmanyam%20Jaishankar%20said%20last%20month%20in%20New%20York%20that%20his%20country%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20examine%20any%20evidence%20presented%20by%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20actually%20been%20badgering%20the%20Canadians.%20We've%20given%20them%20loads%20of%20information%20about%20organized%20crime%20leadership%20which%20operates%20out%20of%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Sikh%20separatists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20situation%20where%20actually%20our%20diplomats%20are%20threatened%2C%20our%20consulates%20have%20been%20attacked%20and%20often%20comments%20are%20made%20(that%20are)%20interference%20in%20our%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20has%20called%20the%20Canadian%20accusations%20over%20the%20killing%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20advised%20its%20nationals%20not%20to%20travel%20to%20certain%20Canadian%20regions%20%26quot%3Bgiven%20the%20increase%20in%20anti-Indian%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20also%20temporarily%20stopped%20processing%20visa%20applications%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%2C%20who%20immigrated%20to%20Canada%20in%201997%20and%20became%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20in%202015%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20two%20masked%20assailants%20in%20the%20parking%20lot%20of%20a%20Sikh%20temple%20near%20Vancouver%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanada%20is%20home%20to%20some%20770%2C000%20Sikhs%2C%20who%20make%20up%20about%20two%20percent%20of%20the%20country's%20population%2C%20with%20a%20vocal%20group%20calling%20for%20creating%20a%20separate%20state%20of%20Khalistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Sikh%20separatist%20movement%20is%20largely%20finished%20within%20India%2C%20where%20security%20forces%20used%20deadly%20force%20to%20put%20down%20an%20insurgency%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Punjab%20in%20the%201980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20Sikh%20protesters%20rallied%20outside%20Indian%20diplomatic%20missions%20in%20Canada%20last%20month%2C%20burning%20flags%20and%20tramp