f%20course%2C%20isn't%20the%20first%20to%20use%20tunnels.%20During%20World%20War%20II%2C%20US%20Marines%20faced%20extensive%20Japanese%20tunnels%20in%20several%20battles%20across%20the%20Pacific%2C%20including%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Iwo%20Jima%2C%20and%20the%20American%20forces%20were%20forced%20to%20clear%20them%20with%20flamethrowers%20and%20hand%20grenades.%20Tunnels%20once%20again%20emerged%20as%20headaches%20for%20the%20US%20military%20a%20few%20years%20later%20during%20the%20Korean%20War%2C%20and%20then%20later%20on%20in%20the%20Vietnam%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Vietnam%2C%20the%20Vietcong%20forces%20built%20a%20huge%20network%20of%20tunnels%20%E2%80%94%20used%20as%20supply%20routes%2C%20to%20store%20ammunition%2C%20and%20to%20house%20infrastructure%20like%20hospitals%20%E2%80%94%20the%20largest%20among%20them%20being%20underneath%20a%20US%20base%20at%20Cu%20Chi.%20Contending%20with%20organized%20guerrilla%20attacks%20on%20the%20base%2C%20the%20American%20forces%20heavily%20bombed%20the%20subterranean%20labyrinth%2C%20but%20that%20wasn't%20enough.%20The%20military%20eventually%20sent%20soldiers%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BTunnel%20Rats%26quot%3B%20down%20there.%20Lightly%20armed%20with%20a%20pistol%20and%20some%20other%20supplies%2C%20they%20faced%20threats%20like%20booby%20traps%2C%20animals%2C%20and%20enemy%20fighters.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20Western%20forces%20dealt%20with%20Islamic%20State%20and%20al-Qaeda%20tunnels%20in%20places%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.army.mil%2Farticle%2F6660%2Fal_qaeda_tunnel_network_destroyed%5C%22%3EIraq%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnews%2Fworldviews%2Fwp%2F2017%2F04%2F14%2Fthe-islamic-state-has-tunnels-everywhere-its-making-them-much-harder-to-defeat%2F%5C%22%3EAfghanistan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202017%2C%20the%20US%20famously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Fmassive-us-bomb-in-afghanistan-killed-36-from-islamic-state-say-local-officials%2F2017%2F04%2F14%2Fdae924e4-20dd-11e7-a0a7-8b2a45e3dc84_story.html%3Fhpid%3Dhp_hp-top-table-main_afghanbomb433am%253Ahomepage%252Fstory%5C%22%3Edropped%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20non-nuclear%20bombs%20it%20has%20%E2%80%94%20the%20GBU-43%20Massive%20Ordnance%20Air%20Blast%20(MOAB)%2C%20or%20Mother%20of%20all%20Bombs%20%E2%80%94%20on%20a%20collection%20of%20ISIS-K%20tunnels%20and%20bunkers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Peshmerga%20fighters%20examine%20the%20entrance%20to%20a%20150-meter-long%20tunnel%20dug%20by%20ISIS%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65313a9b96908fd7cdb26ab4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221996%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeshmerga%20fighters%20examine%20the%20entrance%20to%20a%20150-meter-long%20tunnel%20dug%20by%20ISIS%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Scott%20Peterson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20defensive%20perspective%2C%20Spencer%20said%2C%20Hamas%20can%20use%20its%20tunnels%20to%20protect%20all%20its%20assets%20that%20it%20doesn't%20want%20to%20lose%2C%20such%20as%20personnel%2C%20leadership%2C%20weapons%2C%20communication%20equipment%2C%20ammunition%2C%20and%20supplies.%20The%20group%20could%20also%20use%20them%20to%20move%20the%20200%20hostages%20it%20abducted%20from%20Israel%20during%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20away%20Israel's%20all-seeing%20eye%20and%20strike%20capability%2C%20because%20it%20can't%20hit%20that%20far%20in%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20Spencer%20said.%C2%A0Israel%20has%20been%20heavily%20bombing%20Gaza%2C%20dropping%20thousands%20of%20bombs%20on%20targets%20in%20the%20strip%2C%20but%20the%20tunnels%20are%20harder%20targets%20that%20are%20not%20as%20easily%20destroyed%20as%20surface%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOffensively%2C%20the%20tunnels%20give%20Hamas%20the%20ability%20to%20conduct%20surprise%20attacks%20on%20IDF%20forces%2C%20Spencer%20said.%20This%20includes%20those%20close%20in%20and%20farther%20away%20because%20the%20tunnels%20are%20connected%20to%20rocket%20launch%20points%2C%20such%20as%20pre-set%20setups%20that%20are%20buried%20and%20are%20only%20revealed%20at%20the%20last%20moment%20when%20a%20rocket%20is%20autonomously%20fired.%20In%20other%20cases%2C%20rockets%20are%20brought%20to%20a%20site%20and%20fired%20off%20before%20the%20militants%20head%20back%20underground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%20can%20also%20use%20the%20tunnels%20to%20just%20pop%20up%20near%20IDF%20forces%20in%20a%20style%20of%20guerilla%20warfare%20that%20comes%20as%20a%20complete%20surprise%20and%20retreat%20quickly%20before%20the%20Israelis%20can%20effectively%20return%20fire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPop%20up%2C%20attack%2C%20pop%20back%20down%20in%20the%20ground%2C%20live%20to%20fight%20another%20day%2C%20move%20to%20a%20different%20location%2C%20and%20hit%20them%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20Spencer%20said%20of%20how%20Hamas%20could%20use%20the%20tunnels%20for%20attacks%2C%20likening%20them%20to%20gopher%20or%20mouse%20holes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20IDF%20soldiers%20are%20trained%20in%20advance%20for%20basic%20tunnel%20warfare%2C%20but%20the%20military%20still%20has%20several%20added%20capabilities%20to%20address%20the%20challenges%20in%20Gaza.%20One%20is%20the%20Combat%20Engineering%20Corps'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idf.il%2Fen%2Fmini-sites%2Fthe-hamas-terrorist-organization%2Fthis-is-the-idf-s-plan-to-combat-hamas-terror-tunnels%2F%5C%22%3EYahalom%20Unit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20elite%20band%20of%20commandos%20that%20consists%20of%20several%20different%20specialized%20companies%20handling%20engineering%20reconnaissance%2C%20non-conventional%20weapons%2C%20explosive%20ordinance%20disposal%2C%20and%20tunnel%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Members%20of%20Al-Quds%20Brigades%2C%20an%20armed%20wing%20of%20Islamic%20Jihad%20Movement%2C%20keep%20guard%20at%20tunnels%20on%20Gaza-Israeli%20border%20against%20a%20possible%20attack%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20Gaza%20on%20March%2030%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65313ced96f7540cd06053f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMembers%20of%20Al-Quds%20Brigades%2C%20an%20armed%20wing%20of%20Islamic%20Jihad%20Movement%2C%20keep%20guard%20at%20tunnels%20on%20Gaza-Israeli%20border%20against%20a%20possible%20attack%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20Gaza%20on%20March%2030%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Ashraf%20Amra%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%20also%20has%20other%20tools%20at%20its%20disposal%20as%20well%20for%20fighting%20in%20the%20tunnels%2C%20such%20as%20night-vision%20systems%2C%20drones%20and%20robots%2C%20ground%20and%20aerial%20sensors%2C%20radio%20technologies%2C%20drilling%20equipment%2C%20and%20more%2C%20Spencer%20wrote%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmwi.westpoint.edu%2Funderground-nightmare-hamas-tunnels-and-the-wicked-problem-facing-the-idf%2F%5C%22%3Eanalysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week.%20But%20the%20biggest%20problem%20facing%20the%20IDF%20is%20the%20sheer%20scale%20of%20the%20tunnel%20network%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20silver%20bullet%20to%20mitigate%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20situation%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20finding%20the%20tunnels%20that's%20the%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Spencer%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Israeli%20forces%20can't%20simply%20locate%20the%20problem%2C%20%26quot%3Bblow%20it%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20keeping%20moving.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20know%20what's%20down%20there%2C%20because%20Hamas%20uses%20human%20shields%2C%20because%20Hamas%20has%20a%20hundred-plus%20hostages%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20going%20to%20exponentially%20challenge%20this%20normal%20underground%20nightmare.%26quot%3B