07%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20soldier%20examining%20copper%20plates%20for%20EFPs%20in%20Iraq.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEFPs%20are%20a%20specific%20type%20of%20roadside%20IEDs%20made%20of%20machined%20copper%20placed%20into%20a%20variety%20of%20cheap%2C%20everyday%20objects%2C%20like%20coffee%20cans%2C%20jars%2C%20or%20kitchen%20pots.%20They've%20seen%20frequent%20use%20by%20militias%2C%20terrorists%2C%20and%20guerilla%20forces%20and%20are%20typically%20employed%20as%20asymmetric%20weapons%20against%20larger%20and%20more%20formidable%20targets.%20Iranian-backed%20Shiite%20militias%20used%20them%20during%20the%20war%20in%20Iraq%20following%20the%202003%20US%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20Iranian%20Gen.%20Qassem%20Soleimani%2C%20the%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20Quds%20Force%20commander%20who%20the%20US%20eliminated%20in%20a%20drone%20strike%20nearly%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seattletimes.com%2Fnation-world%2Fsoleimanis-legacy-the-gruesome-high-tech-ieds-that-haunted-u-s-troops-in-iraq%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfamously%20armed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Iraqi%20militias%20with%20EFPs%20and%20trained%20them%20on%20the%20Iranian-engineered%20devices.%20In%20a%20statement%20on%20his%20assassination%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdod-says-us-military-killed-top-iranian-general-qasem-soleimani-2020-1%5C%22%3Eblamed%3C%2Fa%3E%20him%20and%20the%20Quds%20Force%20for%20the%20death%20of%20American%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20activated%2C%20the%20compact%20explosives%20inside%20the%20object%20fire%20the%20copper%20disc%20upwards%2C%20effectively%20turning%20it%20into%20a%20hot%2C%20high-speed%2C%20high-velocity%20munition.%20That%20copper%20projectile%2C%20once%20heated%20by%20explosives%2C%20is%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bslug%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20rapid%20motion%20out%20towards%20the%20target.%20While%20it%20can%20deal%20damage%20over%20a%20few%20dozen%20meters%2C%20EFPs%20are%20far%20more%20accurate%C2%A0and%20destructive%20at%20close%20range%20or%20directly%20beneath%20a%20target%2C%20like%20US%20troops%20saw%20in%20Iraq.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20US'%20invasion%2C%20troops%20reported%20that%20among%20the%20IEDs%20they%20faced%2C%20the%20EFPs%20were%20far%20deadlier%20and%20more%20effective%20than%20other%20roadside%20bombs%20or%20explosives%20they'd%20encountered.%20Soldiers%20said%20EFPs%2C%20hidden%20in%20foam%20blocks%20imitating%20street%20curbs%20and%20rocks%2C%20ripped%20through%20vehicles%20driving%20along%20dirt%20roads%2C%20with%20shards%20of%20the%20copper%20slug%20shredding%20armor%20and%20bodies%20at%20incredible%20speeds.%20One%20former%20Air%20Force%20explosive%20ordnance%20disposal%20officer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2020%2F01%2F03%2Fsoleimanis-legacy-gruesome-high-tech-ieds-that-haunted-us-troops-iraq%2F%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020%20they%20were%20the%20worst%20explosive%20device%20he%20encountered%20during%20his%20time%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statistics%20match%20the%20EFPs'%20deadly%20reputation%2C%20too.%20The%20explosives%20killed%20at%20least%20196%20US%20troops%20and%20wounded%20nearly%20900%20between%202005%20and%202011%2C%20defense%20officials%20said%20in%202015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20challenge%20with%20EFPs%2C%20like%20other%20IEDs%2C%20is%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20to%20locate%20or%20spot%20them%20before%20it%20is%20too%20late%2C%C2%A0given%20they%20may%20look%20like%20ordinary%20objects.%20Another%20challenge%20is%20that%20EFP%20makers%20could%20easily%20change%20the%20bombs'%20designs%20to%20bypass%20American%20vehicle%20countermeasures%20and%20ensure%20the%20slugs%20hit%20their%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20attitude%20and%20approach%20to%20combat%20in%20Iraq%C2%A0likely%20playe