0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20wrote%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20he%20conveyed%20his%20condolences%20at%20the%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%20at%20the%20Al%20Ahli%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20continue%20to%20send%20humanitarian%20assistance%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20Shared%20our%20deep%20concern%20at%20the%20terrorism%2C%20violence%20and%20deteriorating%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20region.%20Reiterated%20India%E2%80%99s%20long-standing%20principled%20position%20on%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1714986693097664745%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20ascribing%20any%20blame%20for%20the%20attack%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1714551508535296439%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1714551508535296439%257Ctwgr%255Ec68d43c0f73b06290a380c0a26171ea298bdcb5e%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fthewire.in%252Fworld%252Fgaza-hospital-blast-india-west-arab-countries-reaction-israel%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20had%20tweeted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20afternoon%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20shocked%20at%20the%20tragic%20loss%20of%20lives%20at%20the%20Al%20Ahli%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExpressing%20condolences%20to%20the%20bereaved%2C%20Modi%20posted%2C%20%E2%80%9CCivilian%20casualties%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20are%20a%20matter%20of%20serious%20and%20continuing%20concern%E2%80%9D%20and%20stated%20that%20those%20%E2%80%9Cinvolved%20should%20be%20held%20responsible%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEchoing%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20on%20Thursday%20reiterated%20concern%20about%20civilian%20casualties%20and%20adherence%20to%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%20but%20yet%20again%20didn%E2%80%99t%20explicitly%20call%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20an%20end%20to%20violence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20weekly%20briefing%2C%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20was%20asked%20whether%20India%20had%20a%20position%20on%20demands%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20West%20Asia%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20seen%20an%20unprecedented%20level%20of%20violence%20and%20deaths%20since%20October%207.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20reply%2C%20he%20pointed%20to%20India%20having%20expressed%20concern%20over%20civilian%20casualties%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20remain%20concerned%20about%20the%20humanitarian%20situation.%20We%20would%20urge%20the%20full%20respect%20and%20strict%20observance%20of%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bagchi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20noted%20that%20India%20had%20%E2%80%9Cstrongly%20condemned%20the%20horrific%20terrorist%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20and%20we%20believe%20the%20international%20community%20must%20stand%20together%20in%20combating%20terrorism%20in%20all%20its%20forms%20and%20manifestations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBagchi%20also%20repeated%20India%E2%80%99s%20Palestine%20policy%20of%20%E2%80%9Cadvocating%20the%20resumption%20of%20direct%20negotiations%20towards%20establishing%20a%20sovereign%2C%20independent%20and%20viable%20State%20of%20Palestine%20living%20within%20secure%20and%20recognized%20borders%2C%20side%20by%20side%20at%20peace%20with%20Israel%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20recounted%20that%20India%20has%20contributed%20%2429.53%20million%20to%20the%20UN%20Relief%20and%20Works%20Agency%20(UNRWA)%20between%202002%20and%202023%20towards%20supporting%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%20work%20in%20Palestine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20annual%20contribution%20to%20UNRWA%20was%20increased%20from%20%241.25%20million%20to%20%245%20million%20in%202018.%20India%20has%20pledged%20annual%20contribution%20of%20%245%20million%20for%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bagchi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20last%20week%E2%80%99s%20briefing%2C%20the%20MEA%20had%20similarly%20sought%20to%20expand%20and%20balance%20the%20Indian%20position%20by%20talking%20about%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%20after%20Modi%20had%20twice%20talked%20of%20only%20solidarity%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-reminds-of-obligation-to-observe-international-humanitarian-law-reiterates-support-for-palestinian-state%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elast%20week%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0said%20last%20week%20that%20New%20Delhi%20believes%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20there%20is%20a%20universal%20obligation%20to%20observe%20international%20humanitarian%20law.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%20that%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cglobal%20responsibility%20to%20fight%20the%20menace%20of%20terrorism%20in%20all%20its%20forms%20and%20manifestations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20MEA%20had%20to%20bring%20some%20additional%20nuance%20into%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20as%20it%20was%20not%20in%20step%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20including%20close%20Arab%20allies%20like%20the%20UAE%2C%20who%20condemned%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20but%20also%20called%20for%20an%20end%20to%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20and%20raised%20the%20demand%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20calls%20for%20ceasefire%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20president%20and%20opposition%20leader%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20repeated%20the%20call%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20an%20immediate%20cease-fire%20and%20for%20humanitarian%20assistance%20to%20the%20beleaguered%20people%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20indiscriminate%20bombing%20on%20the%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20and%20residential%20areas%20resulting%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20hundreds%20of%20lives%20of%20innocent%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20is%20both%20unjustifiable%20and%20a%20grave%20humanitarian%20tragedy%20for%20which%20the%20perpetrators%20must%20be%20held%20accountable%2C%E2%80%9D%20noted%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20repeats%20its%20call%20for%20an%20immediate%20cease-fire%20and%20for%20humanitarian%20assistance%20to%20the%20beleaguered%20people%20of%20Gaza.%20It%20calls%20upon%20all%20sides%20to%20abandon%20the%20path%20of%20senseless%20violence%20and%20war%20and%20begin%20the%20process%20of%20negotiations%20and%20diplomacy%20so%20that%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdAzv3iS6Bb%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FdAzv3iS6Bb%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Congress%20(%40INCIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1714981529464836565%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2019%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20also%20called%20%E2%80%9Cupon%20all%20sides%20to%20abandon%20the%20path%20of%20senseless%20violence%20and%20war%20and%20begin%20the%20process%20of%20negotiations%20and%20diplomacy%20so%20that%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20are%20fulfilled%20and%20the%20security%20concerns%20of%20Israel%20are%20also%20ensured%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20opposition%20party%20had%20condemned%20the%20attack%