017%20km%20stretch%20is%20part%20of%20the%2082%20km%20corridor%20that%20will%20connect%20Delhi%2C%20Ghaziabad%20and%20Meerut.%20It%20will%C2%A0connect%20cities%2C%20towns%20and%20urban%20nodes%20across%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR).%20The%20foundation%20stone%20for%20the%20corridor%20was%20laid%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20in%20March%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmotera-stadium-renaming-narendra-modi-notorious-world-leaders%5C%22%3EAfter%20Lending%20His%20Name%20to%20a%20Stadium%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20Joins%20League%20of%20Notorious%20World%20Leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrains%20on%20the%20RRTS%20network%2C%20christened%20RapidX%2C%20have%20a%20design%20speed%20of%20180%20km%20per%20hour%20and%20an%20operational%20speed%20of%20160%20km%20per%20hour.%20Travel%20time%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Meerut%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1968768%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPM%2520to%2520dedicate%2520to%2520the%2Cwest%2520corridor%2520of%2520Bengaluru%2520Metro%26text%3DPrime%2520Minister%2520Shri%2520Narendra%2520Modi%2Cat%2520around%252011%253A15%2520AM.%5C%22%3Etake%20around%20two%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20section%20between%20Sahibabad%20and%20Duhai%20Depot%20has%20five%20stations%2C%20Sahibabad%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Guldhar%2C%20Duhai%20and%20Duhai%20Depot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fghaziabad%2Ffirst-rrts-train-set-to-be-handed-over-on-sat-to-reach-duhai-soon%2Farticleshow%2F91357650.cms%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20train%20set%20was%20manufactured%20by%20Alstom%20(earlier%20Bombardier)%20and%20will%20be%20able%20to%20seat%20407%20passengers%2C%20while%201061%20can%20commute%20standing.%20The%20trains%20will%20have%20a%202%20by%202%20seating%20capacity%20with%20overhead%20luggage%20racks%2C%20on-board%20Wi-Fi%20and%20charging%20facilities.%20The%20NCR%20Transport%20Corporation%2C%20which%20will%20operate%20the%20network%2C%20has%20ordered%20210%20coaches%20for%20the%20Delhi%20to%20Meerut%20corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20operational%2C%20this%20corridor%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20one%20lakh%20private%20vehicles%20off%20of%20the%20road.%20Wherever%20possible%2C%20RRTS%20stations%20will%20be%20connected%20with%20the%20existing%20modes%20of%20public%20transport%20like%20bus%20stands%2C%20airports%2C%20metro%20and%20railway%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi-Ghaziabad-Meerut%20RRTS%20being%20developed%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%2030%2C000%20crore%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOpposition%20politicians%20slammed%20the%20move%20to%20rename%20the%20trains%20as%20%E2%80%98Namo%20Bharat%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinmool%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Saket%20Gokhale%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20%E2%80%9CModi%E2%80%99s%20fear%20of%20losing%20the%202024%20elections%20%26amp%3B%20his%20desperation%20to%20try%20ANYTHING%20is%20now%20getting%20amusing.%20The%20new%20rapid%20rail%20system%20he%E2%80%99s%20inaugurating%20tomorrow%20has%20been%20named%20%E2%80%98Namo%20Bharat%E2%80%99.%20Insecure%20megalomaniac%20clutching%20at%20straws%20ahead%20of%20his%20impending%20election%20defeat%20by%20INDIA.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20fear%20of%20losing%20the%202024%20elections%20%26amp%3B%20his%20desperation%20to%20try%20ANYTHING%20is%20now%20getting%20amusing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rapid%20rail%20system%20he%E2%80%99s%20inaugurating%20tomorrow%20has%20been%20named%20%E2%80%9CNamo%20Bharat%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInsecure%20megalomaniac%20clutching%20at%20straws%20ahead%20of%20his%20impending%20election%20defeat%20by%20INDIA.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdlAnZ0UOI9%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FdlAnZ0UOI9%3C%2Fa%3