F332607%2Fkerala-pharma-scientist-kenterra-low-cost-solution-waste-management-compost-apartment-complex%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Love%20%E2%80%98Kulhad%20Chai%E2%80%99%3F%20Engineer-Turned-Entrepreneur%20Earns%20Crores%20Selling%20Traditional%20Clay%20Cups%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEver%20sipped%20some%20delightful%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F285468%2Fgrow-organic-oyster-mushrooms-at-home-diy-earthen-pots-how-to%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3E(earthen%20pot)%3C%2Fa%3E%20chai%20on%20a%20%3Cem%3Etapri%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20small%20tea%20stall)%20post%20work%20or%20with%20your%20college%20gang%3F%20For%20us%20tea-loving%20folks%20in%20India%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20wali%20chai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eisn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20drink%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20emotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20have%20you%20ever%20wondered%20where%20our%20beloved%20%3Cem%3Ekulhads%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecome%20from%3F%20Some%20believe%20their%20origin%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20the%20Indus%20Valley%20Civilisation.%20Through%20the%20passage%20of%20time%2C%20these%20little%20pots%20have%20become%20a%20traditional%20alternative%20to%20plastic%20cups%2C%20which%20are%20harmful%20to%20the%20environment%20and%20human%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20had%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20chai%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20that%20it%20came%20from%20one%20of%20Shobhit%20Soni%E2%80%99s%20many%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplants.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cups%20are%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286536%2Ftop-eco-friendly-sustainable-ethical-indian-clothing-brands-suta-okhai-buy-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20sustainable%20and%20eco-friendly%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20during%20delivery%2C%20these%20cups%20would%20crack.%20I%20could%20see%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20market%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20capitalise%20on%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2029-year-old%20says%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20Shobhit%20is%20the%20owner%20of%20Mittisa%20%E2%80%94%20a%20company%20that%20makes%20earthenware%20that%20are%20100%20percent%20sustainable%20and%20eco-friendly.%20With%20his%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%3C%2Fem%3E%20business%2C%20he%20makes%20a%20whopping%20turnover%20of%20Rs%202.76%20crore%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20am%20a%20Marwari%2C%20business%20runs%20in%20my%20veins%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20village%20near%20Ajmer%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Shobhit%20was%20influenced%20by%20businessmen%20all%20around%20him.%20At%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20he%20knew%20he%20wanted%20to%20be%20an%20entrepreneur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20Marwari%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20running%20a%20business%20is%20in%20my%20blood%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20schooling%20at%20a%20local%20school%2C%20Shobhit%20moved%20to%20Pune%20to%20pursue%20a%20degree%20in%20engineering.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20completing%20my%20software%20engineering%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316819%2Fbengaluru-startup-organic-tap-offers-fresh-produce-doorstep-delivery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epursue%20an%20MBA%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20international%20business.%20I%20had%20always%20been%20keen%20on%20utilising%20all%20that%20I%20know%20into%20building%20something%20of%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20making%20%3Cem%3Ekulhads%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20born%20from%20another%20business%20idea%20that%20Shobhit%20pursued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20college%2C%20whenever%20we%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%2C%20we%20would%20locate%20the%20nearest%20%3Cem%3Etapri%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20have%20tea.%20The%20tapri%20vendor%20would%20usually%20have%20glass%20cups%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekulhads%3C%2Fem%3E.%20With%20glass%20cups%2C%20the%20hygiene%20quotient%20is%20really%20low%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20these%20glass%20cups%20are%20usually%20washed%20is%20by%20dipping%20them%20in%20soap%20water%20and%20then%20once%20in%20clean%20water.%20And%20with%20this%2C%20they%20are%20ready%20for%20another%20use.%20I%20always%20preferred%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Eover%20glass%2C%20or%20even%20paper%20cups.%20My%20friends%20would%20prefer%20to%20pay%20more%20for%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Echai%20due%20to%20its%20hygienic%20and%20environmental%20reasons%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad--1697721762.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shobhit%20has%20helped%2045%20plants%20to%20be%20set%20up%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad--1697721762.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad--1697721762-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad--1697721762-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad--1697721762-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad--1697721762-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332621%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShobhit%20has%20helped%2045%20plants%20to%20be%20set%20up%20in%20different%20pa