20sunlight.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20spray%20the%20enzymes%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENita%20says%20it%20takes%20three%20months%20to%20ready%20the%20enzymes.%20It%20has%20the%20aroma%20of%20a%20vinegar.%20After%20the%20batch%20is%20ready%2C%20gardeners%20can%20mix%201-2%20ml%20of%20enzyme%20in%20a%20litre%20of%20water.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20insect%20attack%20is%20severe%2C%20then%20up%20to%205%20ml%20of%20enzymes%20can%20be%20mixed%20in%20the%20water.%20Spray%20this%20mixture%20onto%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20make%20the%20second%20batch%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENita%20says%20that%20these%20enzymes%20can%20be%20stored%20for%20as%20many%20months%20as%20it%20has%20no%20expiry%20date.%20And%20to%20make%20the%20second%20batch%20process%20faster%2C%20one%20can%20add%20roughly%205%20ml%20of%20enzyme%20to%20the%20new%20batch%2C%20so%20it%20will%20then%20be%20ready%20in%20one%20month!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697547131000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332396%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kolkata%20resident%20Nita%20Singh%20started%20gardening%20to%20relive%20childhood%20memories%20of%20her%20grandma%E2%80%99s%20garden.%20Today%2C%20she%20grows%20over%20500%20plants%20of%20diverse%20varieties%20and%20even%20prepares%20her%20own%20bio%20enzymes%20at%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A52%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332396%2Fhow-to-make-bio-enzymes-from-kitchen-waste-at-home-diy-steps-by-kolkata-gardener-nita-singh%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Times%20Indian%20Parents%20Showed%20How%20To%20Advocate%20for%20Rights%20of%20Their%20Children%20in%20LGBTQIA%20Community%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen